# Divvy Config

The latest versions of MacOS have issues with global keyboard shortcuts, which 
prevent Divvy from setting the shortcuts I prefer. There is a way to export 
your config from Divvy on one machine and import it into Divvy on another
machine, however.

## Export
Go to divvy://export/ in a browser. This will pop up Divvy and dump an export
into your clipboard.

## Import
Go to divvy://import/biglonghashedthing in a browser. This will pop up Divvy
and import the config.
